resources.string: Here you will be able to send the secret code you have saved in your lost phone then wait for a message to be sent from the phone lost containg the location back to this phone
እዚህ በስልክዎ ውስጥ ያስቀመጠዎትን ምስጢራዊ ኮድ ለመላክ ይችላሉ ከዚያም ከመልሶው ለመላክ የሚላከውን መልእክት ወደ እዚህ ስልክ በመላክ ያጣሩትን መልዕክት ይጠብቁ.
Here you can save the recovery phone number your are going to use when this phone is lost also you have to insert the secret code
